com.zpaper.cmis.storedobj.api

Interface ObjectStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectStoreImpl

    public interface ObjectStore
    This is the interface an implementation must provide to store any kind of CMIS objects. The ObjectStore is the topmost container of all CMIS object that get persisted. It is comparable to a file system, one object store exists per repository id. The object store allows access objects by an id. In addition a object can be retrieved by path. Typically the object store owns the list of object ids and maintains the path hierarchy.
